      <h2>Where EISS started</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        The first European Initiative for Security Studies conference, convened in January 2017 at
        University Panthéon-Assas, brought together scholars from across Europe to build a shared
        forum for security studies — the founding act of EISS.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Keynote:</strong> Professor Sir Hew Strachan (University of St Andrews). The
        conference was organised around nine permanent thematic sections that the ESSC still tracks
        today.
      </p>
    </article>
